\begin_inset Formula $c_2$
\end_inset

. It can be found 
\begin_inset Formula $|R_{U2R1}(z)| < 1, \forall \real(z) < 0$
\end_inset

, and obviously 
\begin_inset Formula $\lim_{z\rightarrow\infty}R_{U2R1}(z) = 0$
\end_inset

. Therefore, DITR U2R1 method is 
\begin_inset Formula $L$
\end_inset

-stable.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The stability function also shows that for a linear 
\begin_inset Formula $\R$
\end_inset

